pageProduct.description:
General Information

Ashwagandha is an acient herb used for centruies in traditional India Medicine as an a adoptogen and to support balance and wellbeing.  Ashwagandha support reblancing Vata, Vata is one of the three foundation principles of Ayurveda known as doshas.

Warnings

IF SYMPTONS PERSIST TALK TO YOUR HEALTH PROFESSIONAL.  TALK TO AN AYURVEDIC PRACTITIIONER/HEALTH PROFESSIONAL IF YOU ARE UNSURE IF THIS MEDICINE IS RIGHT FOR YOU

Common Uses

ANXIETY, MOOD, ENERGY VITALITY

Ingredients

Each capsule provides
Withania somnifera (Ashwagandha) root dry extract 240mg
Equiv. Withania somnifera root dry 6g

Directions

ONE CAPSULES DAILY OR AS DIRECTED BY YOUR HEALTHCARE PROFESSIONAL
